## Session API
The variable `s` is a session object. Use ONLY these methods:
- s.tap(locate("element description"))       — tap on element
- s.swipe(x1, y1, x2, y2, duration_ms=300)  — swipe gesture
- s.input_text("text")                        — type into focused field
- s.press_key("BACK" | "ENTER" | "HOME")     — press system key
- s.launch_app("package_or_bundle_id")        — launch app

The `locate("description")` function finds an element and returns its bounding box.
It tries DOM rules first; falls back to vision model if not found.

